headline: GTA Online
subtitle: This Week on the Podium: The Vapid Retinue
content:
Make a stop in the lobby of The Diamond Casino & Resort to spin the Lucky Wheel and walk away with GTA$, RP, clothing, accessories, snacks, and all manner of mystery prizes.

This week's podium top prize is the Vapid Retinue â€” a blue-collar workhorse that made a mid-life career switch and became one of the most vaunted rally vehicles of all time. Let it be known that it's never too late to reinvent yourself.
